{"title":"贫农下中农之歌〔歌词〕","authors":["党永庵"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农下中农之歌〔歌词〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党永庵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社红旗展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗照亮好河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好山好水好公社哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿，咱是公社的铁旗杆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风吹不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨浪打不弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身都是胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志冲云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争打头阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产斗争闯在前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳扛大旗不回头呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命意志比钢坚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱国又爱社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重担挑在肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登高望得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红管得宽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金稻银棉手中长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水浇肥千顷田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼看到全世界呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚非拉美心相连！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改造旧世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打扮新河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身硬骨头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代代往下传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子英雄儿好汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永做公社铁旗杆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步紧跟共产党呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳关大道奔向前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}